Rewrapped - Season 2, Episode 10




Ritzy Business

When Recreating the Nabisco RITZ Bits With Cheese, the chefs must be diligent in order to craft this teeny sandwich. In the Innovate Round, a chef breaks down the RITZ Bits to make Pasta Carbonara, but things get dicey when the dough starts to fall apart. The RITZ just keep on coming, on this episode of Rewrapped!




Original Air Date: 29-Nov-2014
